data.title: Anna Torv
data.text:
Name: Anna Charmichael Torv Also Known As: Occupation: actress Medium: Television/Movies Works: Fringe, McLeod's Daughters, The Secret Life of Us, The Pacific Official Website(s): IMDB Fan Website(s): Anna Torv.net Anna Torv Web Anna Torv Online On Fanlore: Related pages

Anna Torv is an Australian actress, born on June 7, 1979 in Victoria, Australia.

She is primarily known for her starring role as Olivia Dunham on the Fox television series Fringe.

She briefly married her Fringe co-star Mark Valley in December 2008 and separated a year later.

Fandom

Stories of RPF often pair Anna Torv with her co-star Joshua Jackson (he plays Peter Bishop). Fans often fancast her as characters.
